# Optional environment overrides for the Hytale systemd unit.
# The baked unit intentionally runs the official launcher script:
#   /var/lib/hytale/game/start.sh
#
# Keep server binaries and mutable state under /var/lib/hytale/game so the
# Hytale Downloader CLI and the server's built-in updater can manage them
# without rebuilding the OS image.
#
# First-run authentication should be done manually as the hytale user:
#   sudo -u hytale /var/lib/hytale/game/start.sh
#
# JVM tuning belongs in:
#   /var/lib/hytale/game/jvm.options
